\v 16 David therefore did as God commanded him: and they smote the host of the
Philistines from Gibeon even to Gazer. 
\v 17 And the fame of David went out into all lands; and the LORD brought the
fear of him upon all nations.
\c 15
\p
\v 1 And \add David\add* made him houses in the city of David, and prepared a
place for the ark of God, and pitched for it a tent. 
\v 2 Then David said, None ought to carry the ark of God but the Levites: for
