\v 11 And David called for Zadok and Abiathar the priests, and for the
Levites, for Uriel, Asaiah, and Joel, Shemaiah, and Eliel, and Amminadab, 
\v 12 And said unto them, Ye \add are\add* the chief of the fathers of the
